title: 2024 전산학부 온라인 개강총회 안내
contents:
[2024 전산학부 온라인 개강총회 안내][Notice for 2024 Online Semester Opening Meeting of SoC][Translated][For Everyone]
Hello everyone
The Executive Committee of the School of Computing has organized the 2024 SoC Semester Opening Meeting for all members of SoC!!
We've curated a wealth of informative content covering academics, career paths, and social activities to enrich your overall school experience, so we eagerly await your interest and participation
Target Audience: Anyone interested in the School of Computing
Zoom Link: bit.ly/soc_opening
Date: 8th of March (Friday) at 18:00
⭐️Program Agenda⭐️
Getting to Know the SoC -> Introducing Executive Committee’s programs -> course roadmaps -> QnA session
We also do an Instagram share event! Come our Insta @in.cs.tagram and join this event!
